pylapp.smoothclicker.android.tools.screen

Class ATScreenWatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • pylapp.smoothclicker.android.tools.screen.AsyncTaskForScreen<java.util.List<PointsListAdapter.Point>,java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>
        • pylapp.smoothclicker.android.tools.screen.ATScreenWatcher

  • public class ATScreenWatcher
extends AsyncTaskForScreen<java.util.List<PointsListAdapter.Point>,java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void>
    Async task which has to check periodically the screen of the device with screen shots. If the just-made-screenshot is the same has a picture in a base, the async task stops itself after having triggered a callback which say the screen matches the picture. Command line to make a screenshot (in adb shell): 
            /system/bin/screencap -p /storage/emulated/legacy/Smooth_Clicker/sc_trigger.png
    Command line to push a picture file: 
            adb push sc_trigger.png /storage/emulated/legacy/Smooth_Clicker/
    Since:
    13/06/2016
    Version:
    1.1.0
